title: Gym Extream - Themeforest Gym and Fitness Wordpress Theme
description:
Gym Extream is a wordpress theme specially designed for Gym and Fitness websites. This template is easy to modify and ready to be up and running out of the box. The PSD files included have been customized to allow fast skinning. 

This template comes in 8 pre made color variations. But it will only take one minute to create your desired color schemes by using theme options

Product Page: http://themeforest.net/item/gym-extream-gym-and-fitness-wordpress-theme/3581558

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
